            <li>AI Integration &amp; Digital Transformation</li>
            <li>Marketing Automation Architecture</li>
            <li>System &amp; Platform Integration</li>
            <li>Sales Infrastructure &amp; Ops Scaling</li>
            <li>Financial Systems Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div><!-- /fw-stages -->
